        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>We're Not Paying You To Break Our Laws Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits making federal funds available to pay for any settlement agreement in any civil action brought as a result of actions taken to enforce the April 6, 2018, Department of Justice memorandum pertaining to the prosecution of cases of improper entry into the United States. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
